### Testes com Token do Better Auth

# O Better Auth retorna o token no body da resposta
# Precisamos enviar esse token como cookie

# Variável com o token
@token = taLdStEHaqXlSNW5GYXGfTwIiAiXGVot

# ========================================
# Teste 1: Token como cookie (padrão Better Auth)
# ========================================

### Dashboard com cookie
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/dashboard
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: better-auth.session_token={{token}}

###

# ========================================
# Teste 2: Token como Authorization header
# ========================================

### Dashboard com Bearer token
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/dashboard
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

# ========================================
# Teste 3: Múltiplos formatos
# ========================================

### Dashboard com ambos
GET http://localhost:3000/admin/dashboard
Content-Type: application/json
Cookie: better-auth.session_token={{token}}
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

